Mazda Motor Corp of Japan reportedcar sales in the U.S. during February of 10,049, down from19,448 during February last year.    The company said year to date car sales in the U.S. totaled21,092, down from 38,441 a year earlier.    Truck sales in the U.S. totaled 8,558 in February, downfrom 9,693 a year earlier. Year to date U.S. truck salestotaled 16,917, compared to 18,341 a year ago. Reuter&#3;